name: s_m_load_msgr_facts_pms_new
description: Session pushed from PC to ICS : s_m_load_msgr_facts_pms_new

parameters.name: $SQ_msgr_facts_pms_new_vw3$
parameters.label: DBConnection_SRC
parameters.customQuery:
SELECT
vw3.Policy_Key_Code,
vw3.Policy_Key,
vw3.Major_Peril_ID,
vw3.Risk_State_ID,
vw3.Inforce_Policy_Key,
vw3.Claim_Key,
vw3.Claim_Type,
vw3.Loss_Cause,
vw3.Loss_Cause_Desc,
vw3.Independent_Adjuster,
vw3.Accident_Dt,
vw3.Reported_Dt,
vw3.Account_Entered_Dt,
vw3.Claim_Paid_Dt,
vw3.Earned_Premium,
vw3.Unearned_Premium,
vw3.Commission_Amt,
vw3.Taxes_Service_Charges,
vw3.Written_Premium,
vw3.Inforce_Premium,
vw3.Loss_Paid_Amt,
vw3.Loss_Paid_Recovery_Amt,
vw3.Loss_Salvage_Amt,
vw3.Loss_Subrogation_Amt,
vw3.Loss_ULAE_Expense,
vw3.Loss_ALAE_Expense,
vw3.Loss_Reserve_Amt,
vw3.Loss_Reserve_For_Incurred_Loss,
vw3.Incurred_Loss_Amt,
vw3.Loss_OS_Adj_Exp,
vw3.annual_statement_line,
vw3.stateline,
nv.row_id,
nv.md5_hash_value 
FROM
 dbo.msgr_facts_pms_new_vw3 vw3
left join dbo.msgr_facts_pms_new_vw nv ON
vw3.policy_key = nv."policy key" AND
vw3.policy_key_code = nv."policy key code" AND
vw3.major_peril_id = nv."major peril id" AND
vw3.risk_state_id = nv."risk state id" AND
coalesce(vw3.inforce_policy_key,'NA') = coalesce(nv."inforce policy key",'NA') and --(can be null)
vw3.account_entered_dt = nv."account entered dt" AND
coalesce(vw3.claim_key,'NA') = coalesce(nv."claim key",'NA') AND --(can be null)
coalesce(vw3.claim_type,'NA') = coalesce(nv."claim type",'NA') AND --(can be null)
coalesce(vw3.loss_cause,'NA') = coalesce(nv."loss cause",'NA') AND --(can be null)
coalesce(vw3.loss_cause_desc,'NA') = coalesce(nv."loss cause desc",'NA') AND --(can be null)
coalesce(vw3.independent_adjuster,'NA') = coalesce(nv."independent adjuster",'NA') AND --(can be null)
coalesce(vw3.claim_paid_dt,'01-01-2008') = coalesce(nv."claim paid dt",'01-01-2008') AND --(can be null)
coalesce(vw3.accident_dt,'01-01-2008') = coalesce(nv."accident dt",'01-01-2008') AND --(can be null)
coalesce(vw3.reported_dt,'01-01-2008') = coalesce(nv."reported dt",'01-01-2008') AND --(can be null)
coalesce(vw3.stateline,'NA') = coalesce(nv."stateline",'NA') AND --(new field; can be null)
coalesce(vw3.annual_statement_line,'NA') = coalesce(nv."annual_statement_line",'NA') --(new field; can be null)
where  vw3.msgr_last_update_date>= (SELECT etlbatchstartst FROM dbo.loadbatchetldt WHERE loadetltype = 'wf_msgr_views')
